text: Ladies over there, what can I do for you?

We have plenty of fresh,
great-value, plump fish~!

Hehe~
today we've got some great horse mackerel in!

They're sparkling, aren't they~?
That's the sign of freshness!

When the chef prepares them as sashimi
and adds ginger, they're delicious~!!

Wow, just hearing about it makes me hungry...!
Kogatan, you're amazing~!

Then, I'll have the recommended
horse mackerel sashimi, please!
Sure thing! Thank you very much!
